In [[Norse cosmology]], '''Alfheim''' ({{Lang-non|Álfheimr}}, "Land Of The Elves" or "Elfland"), also called '''Ljosalfheim''' (''Ljósálf[a]heimr'', "home of the [[Ljósálfar|light-elves]]"), is home of the [[Elf#Old_Norse_texts|Light Elves]].

